channel.title: New rs guides forums! post your server here
channel.description:
Hey guys!!!
me and my friend have made a forum about new servers. I am head admin there and co-owner.
what can we do?
we can put your server out there with its own section and you can post what you want on there!
we also make general RS guides!
this will grow, enjoy!
